ClearPurpose
Our windows and doors are made of
a lot more than glass.
About PGT


All windows and doors can provide a view. But at PGT®, we believe in doing more. It’s why for more than 35 years, our purpose has been providing homeowners with custom windows and doors that fit their unique lifestyle. It’s why we provide unparalleled customer service. Why we build with care and deliver with accuracy. When you choose PGT® Custom Windows + Doors you’re getting a product we trust in our own homes. That’s why we work every day with a clear purpose.









