	About PGT Innovations, Inc.



	 




	PGT INNOVATIONS, INC. (NYSE:PGTI), headquartered in North Venice, Florida, through its wholly-owned subsidiaries, creates products which focus on protecting and enhancing the beauty and functionality of homes and businesses. The Company’s trusted brands include PGT Custom Windows & Doors, CGI Windows & Doors and WinDoor. PGT Innovations, Inc. holds the leadership position in its primary market and is part of the S&P SmallCap 400 Index. For additional information, visit

	http://ir.pgtinnovations.com

	.












	 






