CGI Impact Resistant Windows and Doors
Founded in 1992 to create highly-engineered products for custom applications, CGI Impact Resistant Windows and Doors is now a premier manufacturer of some of the strongest building products on the market. Serving residential and commercial markets in both new and existing construction, CGI’s line of high performance, high aesthetic product offers advanced hurricane protection and technical perfection to complete any design. Our CGI manufacturing and delivery facilities are based in Miami, Florida.
